---
const url = Astro.url.pathname;
const isEnglish = url.includes('/en/');
// 현재 연도를 동적으로 가져옵니다.
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear(); 
---

<footer class="blog-footer">
  {isEnglish ? (
    <>
      <p>© {currentYear} Dayul · <a href="https://lukyday-blog.vercel.app">lukyday-blog.vercel.app</a></p>
      <p>Please credit the source when sharing this post. Unauthorized reproduction is prohibited.</p>
      <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://licensebuttons.net/l/by-nc-nd/4.0/88x31.png" alt="CC BY-NC-ND 4.0" />
      </a>
    </>
  ) : (
    <>
      <p>© {currentYear} Dayul · <a href="https://lukyday-blog.vercel.app">lukyday-blog.vercel.app</a></p>
      <p>이 글을 퍼가실 경우 반드시 출처를 표기해주세요. 무단 전재 및 재배포를 금지합니다.</p>
      <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://licensebuttons.net/l/by-nc-nd/4.0/88x31.png" alt="CC BY-NC-ND 4.0" />
      </a>
    </>
  )}
</footer>